ad_creative_link_descriptions:
Join us this spring for a virtual journey through the European green deal landscape of green certificates and flexibility/aggregators with the Unicorn University Open conference on the topic of European Green Deal enabled by IT, which will take place online on 11.6. We will be talking about current trends and current topics of the energy business. What are the global guarantees of origin trends? What is the role of flexibility for the future of the European energy sectors? And how the IT Technology will support these moves overall. Joinhus on 11th of June.
